<P>
HELP FOR MENTALLY ILL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 I'm writing to thank you for "Return to Reality" by Leslie Earnest (Oct. 18). 
</P>
<P>
 Having a stepson and nephew whom I help with their mental illnesses, I can say 
the piece is accurate, caring, realistic, hopeful and a great public service. 
It will undoubtedly educate many about the victims we see on the street and 
encourage more of us to help where we can. 
</P>
<P>
 KITTY SARKISSIAN 
