</P>
<P>
 Croatia: 40 
</P>
<P>
 Czech Republic: 65 
</P>
<P>
 Macedonia: 35 
</P>
<P>
 Hungary: 55 
</P>
<P>
 Poland: 55 
</P>
<P>
