<TEXT>
<P>
 The Recreation Division has announced its schedule of winter excursions for 
area residents. It includes "A Day at the Races" trip to Santa Anita Park race 
track from 11 a.m. to 6 p.m. Nov. 5.A $16 fee includes admission to the park 
