<DOCNO> LA110194-0146 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 094273 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
November 1, 1994, Tuesday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 20; Column 4; Metro Desk 
</P>
