REGIONAL EARNINGS: VALENCIA NATIONAL BANK REPORTS PROFIT DECLINE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Valencia National Bank posted earnings of $103,492 in the third quarter that 
ended Sept. 30, down 40% from the $170,146 profit the Newhall-based bank 
reported a year earlier. 
</P>
<P>
 For the first three quarters of 1994, Valencia National posted earnings of 
$230,905, compared to year-earlier net income of $86,332. Assets totaled $79.5 
million on Sept. 30, up 14% from $70.1 million on the same date in 1993. 
</P>
<P>
 The three-branch bank said its third-quarter earnings from 1993 were later 
reduced to reflect an accounting change. 
