PEDESTRIAN, 22, IS HIT, KILLED IN ORANGE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 A 22-year-old pedestrian died Monday morning after being struck by a Ford 
pickup truck on Chapman Avenue, police said. 
</P>
