</P>
<P>
 Issue Comparisons 
</P>
<P>
 Orange County adults are more conservative than voters nationwide when 
deciding whether the government should be the provider of last resort. They are 
very much in line with the rest of the country, though, on the need for more 
stringent environmental laws. 
</P>
